        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>As a result of generational war between your peoples, you've trained in special antimagic techniques to battle elven and lashunta spellcasters. You gain a mageslayer claw unarmed attack that deals @Damage[1d6[slashing]] damage, is in the brawling weapon group, and has the finesse, primal, and unarmed traits. A creature you Strike with your mageslayer claw must attempt a Will save against the higher of your class DC or spell DC. On a failure, the creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 1} for 1 minute (or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 2} on a critical failure).</p>"
